        Constructor.
        Parameters:
        numSources - number of source-DataController to prepare array for
        numTargets - number of target-gst.data.DataController to prepare array for
        duplicateSources - if true more than one instance of one specific DataController is allowed in source array
        duplicateTargets - if true more than one instance of one specific DataController is allowed in target array
